{"tid":2395494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登上任後首次: 美國軍艦通過台灣","createTime":"2021-02-05T02:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T03:40:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"893df8c373a458afebdae9df11033ac529c86f32","tid":2395494,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"2021/02/05 05:30<br />\n<br />\n〔記者涂鉅旻／台北報導〕美國總統拜登就任迄今半個月，美軍首派作戰艦航經台灣海峽。一艘伯克級神盾驅逐艦「麥肯號」（DDG-56），昨由北向南航經台灣海峽並繼續向南行駛。國防部表示，因應美艦航經台灣海峽執行「一般航行任務」，國軍運用聯合情監偵作為，全程掌握台灣周邊海、空域相關動態，狀況均正常。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美軍第七艦隊昨發布訊息證實</strong>，通過台灣海峽的軍艦為伯克級神盾驅逐艦「麥肯號」，並強調該艦依照國際法，在本月份第一次通過台灣海峽。這不僅是拜登上任後，首度派軍艦航行台海，也是美國軍艦今年首度航經台海。<br />\n<br />\n根據我國及美國軍方統計，上一次美國軍艦通過台灣海峽，為去年十二月卅一日的麥肯號及柯蒂斯魏柏號（DDG-54）。<strong>去年共有十三起美國軍艦航經台海的紀錄。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1430165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1430165&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ESK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=42b57617\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fpaper%2F1430165&h=0823a986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1430165</a>"},{"pid":"7f3172a1b13ed0ad54126466042a288f99aaf4ff","tid":2395494,"uid":2889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:40:56.000Z","msg":"唔要經過！！要駐守<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91449548eab8916dc4c9905272a7278be6f4a70","tid":2395494,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3172a1b13ed0ad54126466042a288f99aaf4ff","tid":2395494,"uid":2889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:40:56.000Z","msg":"唔要經過！！要駐守<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif